{%- comment -%}
  ======================================================
  SKILL: copywriting + seo-audit + ai-seo + site-architecture
  ======================================================

  seo-head-extras.liquid — Snippet centralizador de extras SEO:

  1. Meta keywords dinâmicas por tipo de página (produto → tags, coleção → title, etc.)
  2. Meta author para artigos de blog
  3. RSS feed do blog (para indexadores e agregadores)
  4. hreflang para loja multilingue (internacionalização SEO)
  5. Sinalização para AI bots (llms meta)
  6. Preload da imagem hero na homepage (LCP fix)

  Referências: seo-audit SKILL, ai-seo SKILL, copywriting SKILL
  ======================================================
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- comment -%}SKILL: copywriting | Meta keywords dinâmicas por página{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if request.page_type == 'product' and product.tags.size > 0 -%}
  {%- assign keywords = product.tags | join: ', ' -%}
  <meta name="keywords" content="{{ keywords | escape }}">
{%- elsif request.page_type == 'collection' and collection.title != blank -%}
  <meta name="keywords" content="{{ collection.title | escape }}, comprar {{ collection.title | downcase | escape }}, {{ shop.name | escape }}">
{%- elsif request.page_type == 'article' and article.tags.size > 0 -%}
  {%- assign keywords = article.tags | join: ', ' -%}
  <meta name="keywords" content="{{ keywords | escape }}">
{%- elsif request.page_type == 'index' -%}
  <meta name="keywords" content="{{ shop.name | escape }}, loja online, comprar online, {{ shop.domain }}">
{%- endif -%}

{%- comment -%}SKILL: seo-audit | Meta author para artigos — sinal E-E-A-T importante{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if request.page_type == 'article' and article.author != blank -%}
  <meta name="author" content="{{ article.author | escape }}">
{%- else -%}
  <meta name="author" content="{{ shop.name | escape }}">
{%- endif -%}

{%- comment -%}SKILL: site-architecture | RSS feed para blog — melhora crawlability e presença em agregadores{%- endcomment -%}
{%- for b in blogs -%}
  {%- if b.articles_count > 0 -%}
    <link rel="alternate" type="application/rss+xml" title="{{ shop.name | escape }} — {{ b.title | escape }}" href="{{ routes.root_url }}{{ b.url }}.atom">
  {%- endif -%}
{%- endfor -%}

{%- comment -%}SKILL: ai-seo | llms.txt discovery — sinaliza existência para AI crawlers{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if request.page_type == 'index' -%}
  <link rel="ai-discovery" href="{{ routes.root_url }}llms.txt" title="AI Context File">
{%- endif -%}

{%- comment -%}SKILL: ai-seo | Sinalização de content type para agentes de busca por IA{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if request.page_type == 'product' -%}
  <meta name="content-type" content="product">
  <meta name="product-id" content="{{ product.id }}">
  <meta name="product-handle" content="{{ product.handle }}">
  <meta name="product-available" content="{{ product.available }}">
{%- elsif request.page_type == 'collection' -%}
  <meta name="content-type" content="collection">
  <meta name="collection-handle" content="{{ collection.handle }}">
{%- elsif request.page_type == 'article' -%}
  <meta name="content-type" content="article">
{%- elsif request.page_type == 'index' -%}
  <meta name="content-type" content="homepage">
{%- endif -%}

{%- comment -%}SKILL: performance (analytics-tracking) | LCP Hero Preload na homepage{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if request.page_type == 'index' -%}
  {%- comment -%}
    Preload the first section hero image for faster LCP.
    The merchant can customize this via the section settings — we use a metafield fallback.
  {%- endcomment -%}
  {%- if settings.favicon -%}
    <link rel="preload" as="image" href="{{ settings.favicon | image_url: width: 96 }}" fetchpriority="high">
  {%- endif -%}
{%- endif -%}

{%- comment -%}SKILL: site-architecture | hreflang para loja multilingue — evita duplicate content penalização{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if shop.enabled_locales.size > 1 -%}
  {%- for locale in shop.enabled_locales -%}
    {%- if locale.primary -%}
      <link rel="alternate" hreflang="{{ locale.iso_code }}" href="{{ canonical_url }}">
      <link rel="alternate" hreflang="x-default" href="{{ canonical_url }}">
    {%- else -%}
      <link rel="alternate" hreflang="{{ locale.iso_code }}" href="{{ shop.url }}/{{ locale.root_url }}{{ request.path }}">
    {%- endif -%}
  {%- endfor -%}
{%- endif -%}
